title: INDOOR.3 | Full Attendance Figures
body_text: If someone told me 19 years ago that ECD gatherings - even just once a year - would produce this much anticipation and pure family fun, my 20 year-old self would've scratched his head. It's 2024 and this past weekend's phenomenal event was easily a Top 10 for yours truly. It had everything, including the competition and nail-bitingly close match-up.
